sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_IterationNumber (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, IterationNumber)

AS IterationNumber
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_IterationMode (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, IterationMode)

SELECT IterState AS IterationMode FROM spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand WHERE (SELECT Iter.Handle FROM Tag AS Tag, RelationTable AS RT, spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand AS Iter WHERE Tag.Name='spirent.methodology.benchmarkstabilityiteratorcommand.11111' AND RT.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle AND RT.SourceHnd=Iter.Handle AND RT.Type='UserTag')

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_SessionRateResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Iteration, IterationMode, Location, EmulationType, Sessions, SessionsUp, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, ConfigSetupRate, SuccSetupRate)

SELECT (SELECT IterationNumber FROM Pppoe_IterationNumber) AS Iteration, (SELECT IterationMode FROM Pppoe_IterationMode) AS IterationMode, Port.Location AS Location, Config.EmulationType AS EmulationType, Sessions, SessionsUp, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, Config.ConnectRate AS ConfigSetupRate, SuccSetupRate FROM PppoePortResults AS Res, PppoxPortConfig AS Config, Port AS Port WHERE Res.ParentHnd = Config.Handle AND Port.Handle = Config.ParentHnd

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_IterationSessionRateResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Iteration, IterationMode, Location, EmulationType, Sessions, SessionsUp, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, SuccSetupRate)

SELECT Iteration, IterationMode, Location, EmulationType, Sessions, SessionsUp, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, SuccSetupRate FROM Pppoe_SessionRateResults WHERE Iteration = (SELECT IterationNumber FROM Pppoe_IterationNumber)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_PortSummaryResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, PortName TEXT, Location, ConfigConnectRate REAL, ExpectedSessions INTEGER, ConnectedSuccessCount INTEGER, DisconnectedSuccessCount INTEGER, FailedConnectCount INTEGER, FailedDisconnectCount INTEGER, SuccSetupRate REAL, MinSetupTime REAL, MaxSetupTime REAL, AvgSetupTime REAL, AvgSuccessTransactionCount INTEGER)

SELECT PR.PortName, Port.Location, PC.ConnectRate AS ConfigConnectRate, PR.Sessions AS ExpectedSessions, PR.ConnectedSuccessCount, PR.DisconnectedSuccessCount, PR.FailedConnectCount, PR.FailedDisconnectCount, SR.SuccSetupRate, SR.MinSetupTime, SR.MaxSetupTime, SR.AvgSetupTime, PR.AvgSuccessTransactionCount FROM PppoxPortConfig AS PC, PppoePortResults AS PR, Port AS Port, Pppoe_IterationSessionRateResults AS SR WHERE PC.Handle == PR.ParentHnd AND PC.EmulationType == 'CLIENT' AND Port.Handle == PC.ParentHnd AND SR.Location = Port.Location

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_IterationSystemSummaryResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, TotalConfigConnectRate REAL, TotalExpectedSessions INTEGER, TotalSuccessConnectCount INTEGER, TotalDisconnectedSuccessCount INTEGER, TotalFailedConnectCount INTEGER, TotalFailedDisconnectCount INTEGER, TotalSuccSetupRate REAL)

SELECT SUM(PC.ConnectRate) AS TotalConfigConnectRate, SUM(PR.Sessions) AS TotalExpectedSessions, SUM(PR.ConnectedSuccessCount) AS TotalSuccessConnectCount, SUM(PR.DisconnectedSuccessCount) AS TotalDisconnectedSuccessCount, SUM(PR.FailedConnectCount) AS TotalFailedConnectCount, SUM(PR.FailedDisconnectCount) AS TotalFailedDisconnectCount, SUM(SR.SuccSetupRate) AS TotalSuccSetupRate FROM PppoxPortConfig AS PC, PppoePortResults AS PR, Pppoe_IterationSessionRateResults AS SR, Port AS Port WHERE PC.Handle == PR.ParentHnd AND PC.EmulationType == 'CLIENT' AND SR.Location = Port.Location AND Port.Handle = PC.ParentHnd

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_SystemSummaryResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Iteration, IterationMode, TotalConfigConnectRate REAL, TotalExpectedSessions INTEGER, TotalSuccessConnectCount INTEGER, TotalDisconnectedSuccessCount INTEGER, TotalFailedConnectCount INTEGER, TotalFailedDisconnectCount INTEGER, TotalSuccSetupRate REAL)

SELECT (SELECT IterationNumber FROM Pppoe_IterationNumber) AS Iteration, (SELECT IterationMode FROM Pppoe_IterationMode) AS IterationMode, TotalConfigConnectRate, TotalExpectedSessions, TotalSuccessConnectCount, TotalDisconnectedSuccessCount, TotalFailedConnectCount, TotalFailedDisconnectCount, TotalSuccSetupRate FROM Pppoe_IterationSystemSummaryResults

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_PortSummaryResults (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Iteration, IterationMode, Location, ConfigConnectRate, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, DisconnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, FailedDisconnectCount, SuccSetupRate, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount)

SELECT (SELECT IterationNumber FROM Pppoe_IterationNumber) AS Iteration, (SELECT IterationMode FROM Pppoe_IterationMode) AS IterationMode, Location, ConfigConnectRate, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, DisconnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, FailedDisconnectCount, SuccSetupRate, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount FROM Pppoe_PortSummaryResults

Properties.Name: Description
Properties.Value: Results Validation to check rate against tolerance.

sql_statement.static: SELECT EnablePercentTolerance, PercentTolerance FROM Pppoe_ThresholdTable

SELECT TotalConfigConnectRate AS 'Total Configured Connect Rate (sessions/s)', TotalExpectedSessions AS 'Total Expected Session Count', TotalSuccessConnectCount AS 'Total Successful Connect Count', TotalDisconnectedSuccessCount AS 'Total Successful Disconnect Count', TotalFailedConnectCount AS 'Total Failed Connect Count', TotalFailedDisconnectCount AS 'Total Failed Disconnect Count', TotalSuccSetupRate AS 'Total Successful Setup Rate (sessions/s)' FROM Pppoe_IterationSystemSummaryResults

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_FailedPorts (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Location, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount, EnablePercentTolerance, PercentTolerance)

SELECT Location, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount, Thr.EnablePercentTolerance AS EnablePercentTolerance, Thr.PercentTolerance AS PercentTolerance FROM Pppoe_PortSummaryResults, Pppoe_ThresholdTable AS Thr WHERE (ConnectedSuccessCount != ExpectedSessions OR FailedConnectCount > 0 OR CASE WHEN Thr.EnablePercentTolerance='TRUE' THEN (SuccSetupRate < ( 1- Thr.PercentTolerance * 0.01) * ConfigConnectRate) or (SuccSetupRate > ( 1 + Thr.PercentTolerance * 0.01) * ConfigConnectRate) ELSE 0 END)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_FailedIterations (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, Iteration, IterationMode, ExpectedSessions, ConnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, ConfigConnectRate, SuccSetupRate, PercentTolerance)

SELECT (SELECT IterationNumber FROM Pppoe_IterationNumber) AS Iteration, (SELECT IterationMode FROM Pppoe_IterationMode) AS IterationMode, SUM(ExpectedSessions) AS ExpectedSessions, SUM(ConnectedSuccessCount) AS ConnectedSuccessCount, SUM(FailedConnectCount) AS FailedConnectCount, SUM(ConfigConnectRate) AS ConfigConnectRate, SUM(SuccSetupRate) AS SuccSetupRate, Thr.PercentTolerance AS PercentTolerance FROM Pppoe_FailedPorts, Pppoe_ThresholdTable AS Thr

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_IteratorEndState (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, EnableStabilityBackoff, SearchMinVal, SearchMaxVal, StabilityRepeatCount, StabilityBackoffStep, StabilitySuccessPercent, IsConverged, ConvergedVal, FoundStableValue, StableValue)

SELECT EnableStabilityBackoff, MinVal AS SearchMinVal, MaxVal AS SearchMaxVal, RepeatCount AS StabilityRepeatCount, StepVal AS StabilityBackoffStep, SuccessPercent AS StabilitySuccessPercent, IsConverged, case when ConvergedVal = '' then 'No converged rate found' else ConvergedVal end as ConvergedVal, FoundStableValue, case when StableValue = '' then 'No stable rate found' else StableValue end as StableValue FROM spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand WHERE (SELECT Iter.Handle FROM Tag AS Tag, RelationTable AS RT, spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand AS Iter WHERE Tag.Name='spirent.methodology.benchmarkstabilityiteratorcommand.11111' AND RT.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle AND RT.SourceHnd=Iter.Handle AND RT.Type='UserTag')
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_ScaleResult (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, IsConverged, ConvergedVal)
SELECT IsConverged, ConvergedVal FROM Pppoe_IteratorEndState
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_StabilityResult (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, EnableStabilityBackoff, FoundStableValue, StableValue)
SELECT EnableStabilityBackoff, FoundStableValue, StableValue FROM Pppoe_IteratorEndState
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Pppoe_StabilityScaleValueResult (ID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, StabilityScaleValueResult)

SELECT (CASE WHEN ES.EnableStabilityBackoff=1 THEN (CASE WHEN Stability.FoundStableValue=1 THEN Stability.StableValue ELSE 0 END) ELSE (CASE WHEN Scale.IsConverged=1 THEN Scale.ConvergedVal ELSE 0 END) END) AS StabilityScaleValueResult FROM Pppoe_IteratorEndState AS ES, Pppoe_StabilityResult AS Stability, Pppoe_ScaleResult AS Scale

sql_statement.static: SELECT SearchMinVal AS 'Search Minimum Rate (sessions/s)', SearchMaxVal AS 'Search Maximum Rate (sessions/s)', (CASE WHEN EnableStabilityBackoff = 1 THEN 'True' ELSE 'False' END) AS 'Enable Stability Backoff', StabilityRepeatCount AS 'Stability Repeat Count', StabilityBackoffStep AS 'Stability Backoff Step', StabilitySuccessPercent AS 'Stability Backoff Success (%)', PercentTolerance as 'Session Rate Tolerance (%)', ExpectedSessionRate as 'Session Rate Threshold (sessions/s)' FROM Pppoe_IteratorEndState, Pppoe_ThresholdTable, Pppoe_SessionRateThresholdTable

SELECT Iteration AS 'Iteration', (case when TotalSuccSetupRate < ( 1 - (select PercentTolerance from Pppoe_ThresholdTable) * 0.01) * TotalConfigConnectRate  or TotalSuccSetupRate > ( 1 + (select PercentTolerance from Pppoe_ThresholdTable) * 0.01) * TotalConfigConnectRate or TotalFailedConnectCount > 0 or TotalSuccessConnectCount != TotalExpectedSessions then 'FAIL' else 'PASS' end ) as 'Verdict', (CASE WHEN IterationMode='SEARCH' THEN 'Binary Search' ELSE 'Stability' END) AS 'Test Phase', TotalConfigConnectRate AS 'Total Config Rate (sessions/s)', TotalExpectedSessions AS 'Total Expected Session Count', TotalSuccessConnectCount AS 'Total Successful Connection Count', TotalFailedConnectCount AS 'Total Failed Connection Count', TotalFailedDisconnectCount AS 'Total Failed Disconnect Count', TotalSuccSetupRate AS 'Total Successful Setup Rate (sessions/s)' FROM Pppoe_SystemSummaryResults
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS PPPoEScaleSessionRate (ConvergedSessionRate INTEGER, StableSessionRate INTEGER, ExpectedSessionRate INTEGER)
SELECT (CASE WHEN (select IsConverged from Pppoe_ScaleResult) = 0 THEN 'Did not converge' ELSE (select ConvergedVal from Pppoe_ScaleResult) END) AS 'ConvergedSessionRate',

(select case when EnableStabilityBackoff = 0 then 'Stability test disabled' when EnableStabilityBackoff = 1 and FoundStableValue = 0 then 'No stable session rate found'  when EnableStabilityBackoff = 1 and FoundStableValue > 0 then StableValue end from Pppoe_StabilityResult) AS StableSessionRate,
(select ExpectedSessionRate from Pppoe_SessionRateThresholdTable) AS ExpectedSessionRate
